{
  "total_duration": 739.015,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.88,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everything except the weather"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“唯独没有考虑到天气”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 7.23,
      "end": 19.07,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是一个简单的“天气不好”故事。它讲的是 dream life 和 daily life 的落差：一个人计划了退休、乡村、房子，却忘了每天都会碰到的气候。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 19.42,
      "end": 32.355,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Harrison had lived in the Mediterranean for many years before he returned to England."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mediterranean"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是一个国家，而是地中海周围的一片地区。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 32.705,
      "end": 46.785,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的 Mediterranean 让人想到 sunshine, warm days, sea views, walking outside, outdoor cafes。天气不是背景板，它会改变人的衣服、出门、心情和日常 routine。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 47.135,
      "end": 55.855,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Harrison 在这种 sunshine 里住了很多年，所以他回英国乡村时，不只是换了一个地址，而是换回了另一种 daily climate。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 56.205,
      "end": 64.005,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他 dreamed of retiring in England，planned to settle down in the country，还很快 bought a house。听起来一切都想好了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 64.355,
      "end": 70.219,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是现实来得很快："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Almost immediately he began to complain about the weather."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 70.569,
      "end": 83.168,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课的三个情绪词特别重要："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "immediately"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是几乎马上，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "continually"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一直反复，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bitterly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是冷得刺人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 83.518,
      "end": 100.358,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：Mediterranean -> dreamed of England -> settle down -> bought house -> immediately complained -> continually rained -> bitterly cold -> shock -> could not bear -> sold house -> dream ended -> except the weather。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 100.708,
      "end": 110.74,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 Harrison 的 long dream。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My old friend, Harrison, had lived in the Mediterranean for many years before he returned to England."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 111.09,
      "end": 117.954,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had lived"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 past perfect，说明他回英国以前，已经在 Mediterranean 住了很多年。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 118.303,
      "end": 127.463,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那里的 sunshine 不只是好看的阳光，也是一种生活方式：可以散步、坐在外面、靠近海边，衣服和日程都比较轻松。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 127.813,
      "end": 134.453,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文接着说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had often dreamed of retiring in England and had planned to settle down in the country."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 134.803,
      "end": 143.971,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "retire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是工作多年后退休；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "settle down"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是在一个地方安顿下来，过稳定生活。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 144.321,
      "end": 153.201,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以第一幅画要看见这个对比：Harrison 身在地中海阳光里，脑子里想的是 English country retirement。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 153.551,
      "end": 161.063,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是梦想变成行动。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had no sooner returned than he bought a house and went to live there."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 161.412,
      "end": 169.068,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "no sooner... than..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的感觉是“一刚发生 A，就发生 B”。他刚回英国，就买房住了进去。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 169.418,
      "end": 175.978,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这说明 Harrison 很确定自己想要什么：retirement, country house, quiet life。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 176.328,
      "end": 184.848,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但这也是问题所在。他 planned the place, but not the climate。他看见了 country house 的画面，却没有认真想 daily weather。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 185.198,
      "end": 198.958,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以把这一步想成现代生活里看视频做决定：一个地方看起来 beautiful, peaceful, perfect，可是还没有检查交通、学校、食物、朋友、网络，还有天气。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 199.308,
      "end": 210.612,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是 weather shock。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Almost immediately he began to complain about the weather, for even though it was still summer, it rained continually and it was often bitterly cold."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 210.962,
      "end": 218.57,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "immediately"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是普通的 soon，而是 almost at once。梦想刚落地，现实就开始打脸。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 218.919,
      "end": 228.959,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "continually"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是 one rainy afternoon，而是雨一直下、反复下，影响 walking, clothes, travel, outdoor plans, and mood。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 229.309,
      "end": 240.141,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bitterly cold"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也不是 a little cold。它是冷得刺人、冷得发苦，尤其对一个住惯了 sunshine 的人来说，非常难受。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 240.491,
      "end": 245.775,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After so many years of sunshine, Harrison got a shock."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 246.125,
      "end": 252.285,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个 shock 不是说英国不好，而是说 Harrison 的身体和习惯已经被另一种 climate 改变了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 252.635,
      "end": 258.947,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是梦想结束。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He acted as if he had never lived in England before."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 259.296,
      "end": 267.232,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as if"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 as though，好像怎样。Harrison 的反应像是从来没在英国生活过一样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 267.582,
      "end": 275.97,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In the end, it was more than he could bear."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bear"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 endure，忍受。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 276.32,
      "end": 283.344,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后来了很快的反转："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had hardly had time to settle down when he sold the house and left the country."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 283.694,
      "end": 292.182,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hardly... when..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的感觉是“几乎还没来得及 A，就 B 了”。他还没真正安顿下来，就卖房离开了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 292.531,
      "end": 297.707,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后的 punchline 是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Harrison had thought of everything except the weather."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 298.057,
      "end": 307.705,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他计划了 dream picture，却忘了 daily feeling。标题里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "except"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 not including，唯独漏掉的那一项。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 308.055,
      "end": 310.575,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最容易误会的地方是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 310.925,
      "end": 314.124,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "以为它是在说 England has bad weather？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 314.474,
      "end": 325.834,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，但我们不要这样讲。问题不是 England bad，而是 Harrison 从 Mediterranean sunshine 回到 cool, wet, changeable weather，落差太大。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 326.184,
      "end": 328.624,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么要解释 Mediterranean？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 328.974,
      "end": 338.454,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它不是一个国家名。课文用它来带出 climate and lifestyle：sunshine, warmer days, outdoor life, sea-side feeling。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 338.804,
      "end": 343.532,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那 weather 为什么这么重要？不就是下雨和冷吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 343.882,
      "end": 354.962,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对游客来说可能只是一天的感受。对 resident 来说，weather 会决定穿什么、怎么出门、能不能散步、心情怎么样、每天的 routine 怎么安排。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 355.312,
      "end": 357.2,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "三个 adverbs 呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 357.55,
      "end": 371.229,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它们是这课的 language feel。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "immediately"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让现实来得很快；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "continually"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让雨变成 daily pressure；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bitterly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让冷有身体上的刺痛感。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 371.579,
      "end": 373.841,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以 Harrison 是傻吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 374.191,
      "end": 383.071,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。他的错误很 human：他记得 the idea of England，却忘了 actually living there every day 的感觉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 383.421,
      "end": 389.565,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My old friend, Harrison, had lived in the Mediterranean for many years before he returned to England."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 389.915,
      "end": 394.955,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had often dreamed of retiring in England and had planned to settle down in the country."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 395.305,
      "end": 399.601,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had no sooner returned than he bought a house and went to live there."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 399.951,
      "end": 408.327,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Almost immediately he began to complain about the weather, for even though it was still summer, it rained continually and it was often bitterly cold."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 408.676,
      "end": 412.732,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After so many years of sunshine, Harrison got a shock."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 413.082,
      "end": 416.778,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
