    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 484.954,
      "end": 495.314,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "continually"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "一场雨不是问题。Continual rain 会改变日常生活：出门要带伞，路是湿的，衣服不容易干，walking 和 outdoor plans 都会被打断。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 495.664,
      "end": 502.803,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "continually"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "continually"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让 weather 从一个场景，变成每天都压在生活上的 pressure。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 503.153,
      "end": 505.905,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "bitterly"
      },
      "segments": [
