    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 540.988,
      "end": 548.548,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 不要背成机械时态表。它其实在讲 long-before dream and quick-after collapse。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 548.898,
      "end": 561.277,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组是 long-before dream："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had lived"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had often dreamed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had planned"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ", 还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the dream he had had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 561.627,
      "end": 571.387,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Past perfect 说明这些事情都在主要故事动作之前已经存在：他住过很多年，梦想了很多年，计划也早就形成了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 571.737,
      "end": 577.201,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组是 too fast："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had no sooner returned than he bought a house."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 577.551,
      "end": 585.031,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话让动作非常快：returned, bought, went to live there。决定太快，检查太少。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 585.381,
      "end": 591.501,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组也是 too fast："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had hardly had time to settle down when he sold the house."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 78,
