      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中间的 weather feel 用三个词推动故事："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "immediately"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "continually"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bitterly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 80,
      "start": 607.518,
      "end": 614.01,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "except"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "收住："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He had thought of everything except the weather."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 81,
      "start": 614.36,
      "end": 627.5,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以语法板可以这样记：had lived / had dreamed / had planned 是多年梦想；no sooner 和 hardly 是崩塌太快；except 是最后漏掉的 daily detail。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 82,
      "start": 627.849,
      "end": 637.969,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进你的生活。想象你看到一个 beautiful place 的视频，很想搬去那里，或者参加一个 new school, camp, or activity。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 83,
      "start": 638.319,
      "end": 644.159,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你不能只说 it looks beautiful。你要像 Harrison 的反面一样，检查 daily details。"
